<para style="q1">

<verse number="24" style="v" />Pour out your indignation on them,</para>

<para style="q1">and let the fierceness of your anger overtake them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="25" style="v" />Let their place be a desolation;</para>

<para style="q1">let no one live in their tents.</para>
